values: The move is a total nightmare! Cat's job is fucking about with the transfer so don't even know when we're moving- we have half the flat in boxes 'cause we're supposed to be in london now!! We no longer have internet 'cause it 'isn't worth renewing the contract for a couple of weeks' says Cat who actually has internet access at work :p Well, hopefully, I'll be back at some stage... I can't live in the dark ages forever...

'The world is going to be destroyed
but there's no point in getting all annoyed...'

Saw Hiitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy this week- the dolphin song keeps getting stuck in my head!!

Well, I'm only slightly hungover today. Hiding out on the net because Cat keeps hinting that we need get on with our flat hunt. Is there anything worse than flat-hunting? She'll be trying to get me to start packing next! Bit worried about the move. Amoungst other things, I'm not sure how well Bailey (our kitty) will take it. Just hoping he'll adjust to london ok :-/

Hmmm does this mint choc chip colour scheme make anyone else hungry!? Yum ice cream!

Going out pubbing later- just an excuse to wear my new corset and get slightly drunk :)
